ed the temporary substitution of “or authorized representative of a community” for “or any other interested domestic party”, was executed by making the temporary substitution for “or any other interested domestic party” the second time appearing to reflect the probable intent of Congress. See Codification note above and Effective and Termination Dates of 2009 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–5","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1873(b)(1)(A), 1893, temporarily inserted “or 2401e” after “section 2401b”. See Codification note above and Effective and Termination Dates of 2009 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2004—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/429/s2004/a/11/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–429, § 2004(a)(11)(A)","children":[],"tail":", amended directory language of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/210/s142/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–210, § 142(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":". See 2002 Amendment notes below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2002—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/210/s142/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–210, § 142(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", as amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/429/s2004/a/11/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–429, § 2004(a)(11)(A)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “an agricultural commodity producer (as defined in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2401/2"},"text":"section 2401(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":") aggrieved by a determination of the Secretary of Agriculture under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2401b"},"text":"section 2401b of this title","children":[],"tail":",” after “"},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2341"},"text":"section 2341 of this title","children":[],"tail":",” in first sentence and substituted “, the Secretary of Commerce, or the Secretary 